  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "For the three datasets respectively, the 2$\\sigma$ individual confidence intervals of $r_e$ or [3.14, 3.33], [2.40, 2.57] and [0.20, 0.38], and of n are [4.16, 4.45], [2.31, 2.52] and [10.2, 13.4]."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "def S1(I, r, I_0, r_e, n):\n",
    "    cost = 0.0\n",
    "    for i in range(len(r)):\n",
    "        cost += I[i] - func3(r[i], I_0, r_e, n)\n",
    "    return cost\n",
    "bestr_e = myFit31.best_values['r_e']\n",
    "bestn = myFit31.best_values['n']\n",
    "bestI_0 = myFit31.best_values['I_0']\n",
