    "## Task 3: Supernovae"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "A supernova is a violent explosion of a star which makes it temporarily so luminous that it can be seen from huge distances."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 68,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JorisDeRidder/DataAnalysisInPhysicsAndAstronomy/main/Images/supernovaNGC2525.jpg\" width=\"700\"/>"
      ],
      "text/plain": [
