   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "The columns in the table are:\n",
    "- **z**: the redshift of the supernova\n",
    "- **mu**: the distance modulus [mag]\n",
    "- **sigma**: the uncertainty on the distance modulus [mag]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 71,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
